Package: SocialFractal
Title: Analyze Multilevel Social Network and Fractal Egocentric Network Structures
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    c(person("Yixuan", "Zhang", , "yxuan_zhang@outlook.com", role = c("aut", "cre")),
      person("Daiping", "Wang", , "wangdaiping@ioz.ac.cn", role = "aut"),
      person("Damien", "Farine", , "damien.farine@ieu.uzh.ch", role = "aut"))
Description: This package provides tools for analyzing multilevel social network and 
    fractal egocentric network structures, including functions to compute clumping rates, 
    calculate group sizes, and detect communities. It leverages network analysis techniques 
    to quantify the hierarchical organization of social interactions.
